data.description:
Immaculate move-in ready villa in St. Andrews Park! 2/2 plus a den/poss 3 bedroom/flex space. High end finishes, crown molding, 10ft ceilings, 8 ft doors, 42 inch kitchen cabinets, granite, bar stool seating, undermount stainless sink, large pantry, wainscoting in living room, plantation shutters, impact windows, fenced yard, 2 car garage with attic storage, steps from the community pool.Primary bedroom with walk-in closet, dual sinks in bath. Desirable community with great amenities, easy walk to Publix Plaza and convenient to access major highways/roads, golf, entertainment, beaches and restaurants. HOA fee covers roof and exterior maintenance, lawn care, security gate, cable/wifi, pool, hot tub, clubhouse and fitness center. It's your time to enjoy resort style, low maintenance living. Come see this exceptional home!
Interested buyers are encouraged to confirm all details and consult HOA and management company.
